---
title: Chorizo Topped Beef Enchiladas with smashed avocado and potato wedges
description: Bean and beef enchiladas are topped with spiced chorizo, melted cheese and smashed avocado all served with sumptuous potato wedges in this larger-than-life and incredibly tasty easy-to-prepare meal.
